        Narrative Plan:
        1. Intro: Define the "Shield and Sword" strategy.
        2. Tiers Visualized: Compare the CPC costs (Bar Chart).
        3. Strategic Matrix: Radar chart comparing Risk vs Reward vs Cost for each tier.
        4. Timeline: Gantt chart for the 30-day rollout.
        5. Conclusion: Summary of the decision matrix.
        
        Chart Selection Justification (NO SVG):
        1. Cost Comparison -> Bar Chart (Chart.js): Best for comparing quantitative values (money) across categories.
        2. Strategic Trade-offs -> Radar Chart (Chart.js): Excellent for multivariate comparison (Risk, Cost, Impact) of the 3 tiers.
        3. Roadmap -> Horizontal Floating Bar Chart (Chart.js): Effective for showing time duration (Gantt style) without needing SVG.
        
        NO SVG / NO MERMAID CONFIRMED.
